      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i just cut my arm pretty bad while cooking. its a deep one and its still oozing blood even though i've been pressing on it for a bit. i dont really wanna go to the hospital/dr if i dont have to... would it be okay if i just put some honey on it and wrap it up? i heard that helps things heal better naturally",
